snippet.title: Dungeon Defenders Going Rogue - Early Access Now Available!
snippet.description:
Check out the newest addition to the Dungeon Defenders Universe! Delve deep into familiar dungeons, battle waves of enemies, and defeat reimagined bosses in this roguelite adventure!

Play Dungeon Defenders Going Rogue now!
Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1815530/

More details here: https://bit.ly/DDGRInfo

Watch our Devstreams on Twitch!
http://www.twitch.tv/Chromatic_Games

Follow Dungeon Defenders Going Rogue and Chromatic Games!
http://www.dungeondefenders.com
http://www.facebook.com/dungeondefenders
